  "content": "<p data-pid=\"xlPz5YBT\">这一事实看上去很容易。那么，我们为什么会一遍又一遍地想当然，固执己见，一遍又一遍地犯下相同的错误呢？为什么我们如此不善于习得精确无误的信念，而又要如何才能做得更好？这七个系列讨论了动机性推理与确认偏差，尤其是难以察觉的自欺欺人和「像士兵一样争论」。</p><p data-pid=\"FnAYP2Hm\">——<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.readthesequences.com/Biases-An-Introduction\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">《偏见：序言》</a><sup data-text=\"前言+导读\" data-url=\"https://hpmor.xyz/ai2zb_0/\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup>by Rob Bensinger</p><hr/><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/827867654\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"理性：序言\" data-draft-cover=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-52b323f664f6af45cbdffbe5bc602b8d.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">理性：序言</a><h2>E. 过于方便的借口</h2><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/991304319\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"过于方便的借口\" data-draft-cover=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-eb16b34c242bf59997738a371a8063ba.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">过于方便的借口</a><h2>F. 政治与理性</h2><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/7906110908\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"政治与理性\" data-draft-cover=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-db9af3f23d2b28e7493f396f4a7bee29.webp?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">政治与理性</a><h2>G. 反对合理化</h2><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/30664297001\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"反对合理化\" data-draft-cover=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-7980b0d9fc1a0b21a8d2754e42fe0631.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">反对合理化</a><h2>H. 反对双重思想</h2><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1907400677073852024\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"反对双重思想\" data-draft-cover=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8d169939bcc4634919330ca52d2b2e52.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">反对双重思想</a><h2>I. <span class=\"nolink\">用新眼光看问题</span></h2><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1946993902033835772\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"用新眼光看问题\" data-draft-cover=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-1cf5d4300af436ccf56b8f5c549faa47.png?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">用新眼光看问题</a><h2>J. <span class=\"nolink\">死亡螺旋</span></h2><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/2004588162681427313\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"死亡螺旋\" data-draft-cover=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-887be012886f5d556f75ff858ce30b1d.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">死亡螺旋</a><h2>K. 放手</h2><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/2015473376601327376\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"放手\" data-draft-cover=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-0f68089076297461a8b131bf829f051c.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">放手</a><hr/><blockquote data-pid=\"uLNCC96E\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//paratranz.cn/projects/3131\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Thoughts Memo</a> 汉化组译制<br/>原文：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.readthesequences.com/Book-II-How-To-Actually-Change-Your-Mind\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Book II: How to Actually Change Your Mind | Rationality: From AI to Zombies</a></blockquote>",
